=Description=

"Just finished listening to this panels from SXSW Interactive 2006 and one of the many interesting topics that caught my attention was the important of machine readable meta data as an aspect of the creative commons license. This allows search engines to sift through the pool the Creative Commons licensed content and return results based on a desired license."
(http://www.outklass.com/?p=51)

